<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .details { background: #fff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
      .message-box { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1 style="color: #007bff; margin: 0;"><%= @greeting %></h1>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">Thank you for reaching out to Wrantle</p>
      </div>

      <div class="details">
        <p>We've received your <%= @contact.contact_type.humanize.downcase %> request. Here's a summary of what you submitted:</p>

        <div class="message-box">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Contact Details</h2>
          <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @contact.name %></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @contact.email %></p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= @contact.phone %></p>
          
          <% if @contact.contact_type == "schedule_chat" %>
            <h2>Preferred Meeting Time</h2>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @contact.preferred_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @contact.preferred_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></p>
          <% end %>

          <h2>Your Message</h2>
          <p><%= @contact.message %></p>
        </div>

        <% if @contact.contact_type == "schedule_chat" %>
          <p>We'll review your preferred meeting time and confirm the schedule shortly.</p>
        <% elsif @contact.contact_type == "request_info" %>
          <p>We'll gather the information you need and get back to you soon.</p>
        <% else %>
          <p>We'll review your needs and provide a detailed assessment shortly.</p>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Wrantle Team</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8em; color: #888;">
          If you did not submit this request, please contact us immediately at support@wrantle.com
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>